33:25.962 --> 33:27.589
Nancy Drew.

33:27.589 --> 33:29.466
What's that old saying?

33:29.466 --> 33:32.010
Where there's smoke,
there's a miscreant teen sleuth

33:32.010 --> 33:33.803
who's about to be arrested?

33:32.010 --> 33:33.803
NICK:

33:32.010 --> 33:33.803
Arrested?

33:33.803 --> 33:36.014
