34:00.121 --> 34:01.873
Nancy.

34:01.873 --> 34:04.251
Gilbert.

34:04.251 --> 34:07.170
Your chariot awaits.

34:24.771 --> 34:27.190
I can't believe
you fell asleep on the job.

34:27.190 --> 34:30.527
Easiest $950 we ever made.

34:30.527 --> 34:32.112
(both chuckle)

34:38.827 --> 34:40.453
Let me guess.

34:40.453 --> 34:42.455
Tacking on a few more
charges? See what sticks?

34:42.455 --> 34:44.249
Nope.

34:44.249 --> 34:46.042
Please turn around.

34:50.463 --> 34:51.589
