I really care about.

39:11.808 --> 39:14.936
'Cause I've never had a crew

39:14.936 --> 39:17.397
like us.

39:17.397 --> 39:20.191
I'm not gonna let us die.

39:20.191 --> 39:22.193
I never doubted that.

39:23.403 --> 39:24.696
So, you're still mad?

39:25.905 --> 39:28.658
I'm scared.

39:29.951 --> 39:32.870
Sometimes
you just have to let fear be.

